---
import SectionLabel from "@/components/SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section class="px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 py-24 w-full">
  <div class="max-full">
    <SectionLabel number="01" label="About" />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-24">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif leading-tight">
          8+ years crafting<br />
          <em class="text-teal italic">digital products</em><br />
          that scale.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          My work sits at the intersection of <strong class="text-foreground">backend systems</strong>,{" "}
          <strong class="text-foreground">distributed architecture</strong>, and{" "}
          <strong class="text-foreground">frontend engineering</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Currently at <a href="https://vercel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-teal hover:underline">Vercel</a>,
          building developer tools and infrastructure that powers millions of deployments.
        </p>

        <p>
          Previously shipped products at startups and Fortune 500 companies alike.
          Open source contributor and occasional writer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
